{"tid":866271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"早幾日去左高鐵站，包膠","createTime":"2018-10-17T17:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T05:26:15.000Z","uid":73915,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa2a7df68e63640c64324ff76185cd5ba962dd3","tid":866271,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"早幾日諗住去睇下一千億搞左d乜柒出黎<br />\n就去左高鐵站<br />\n一入去，屌你老母成陣除，好似太子站咁<br />\n分唔撚到係裝修，蝗味，定其他臭味<br />\n跟手望下賣飛果度，一鄂高頭<br />\n個列車班次牌，隻碌柒藍搞到我以為未買飛已經到左廣州<br />\n你老味入面d裝修仲柒過深水埗地鐵站<br />\n隻地磚以為去左廁所<br />\n跟住果幾碌奇型怪狀幾主力柱，冇美感又礙眼<br />\n然後去左綠化廣場，望埋個山墳建築，果d一格格玻璃真係好撚肉酸<br />\n我好難想像一千億搞左舊咁既野出如果機場係8分，呢件垃圾最多2分<br />\n真係好撚肉酸<br />\n去翻隔離圓方根本係天堂與地獄<br />\n一千億已落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab364d9c205e31f30c3f7a0cd627ae5e4e595cbe","tid":866271,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:37:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 高鐵站真係有陣大陸除<br />\n仲傳到柯士甸站都有<br />\n極度懷疑黨想係人類五感上慢慢侵蝕香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n極高招，啲連鎖酒店都會用同一種香水/消毒藥水令到啲客人覺得好有親切感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n潛移默化⋯"},{"pid":"2f325c51dbfd6cbea01dddc894304be429b5e667","tid":866271,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab364d9c205e31f30c3f7a0cd627ae5e4e595cbe","tid":866271,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:37:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 高鐵站真係有陣大陸除<br />\n仲傳到柯士甸站都有<br />\n極度懷疑黨想係人類五感上慢慢侵蝕香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n極高招，啲連鎖酒店都會用同一種香水/消毒藥水令到啲客人覺得好有親切感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n潛移默化⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"最終目標係傳到全香港都係果隻味<br />\n之後一放毒氣 陷港剷...<br />\n高招！"},{"pid":"cc910ce0ccde5025b2c660c2c94754023f06eecb","tid":866271,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:55:25.000Z","msg":"個站頭幾日已經殘到仆街<br />\n啲地下好多跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414710e1ccaa3e399572a1c99096caccd45ae62e","tid":866271,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"感覺好似喺大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bcc5f245b478ab656d68e0612fd70fbed9502b","tid":866271,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc910ce0ccde5025b2c660c2c94754023f06eecb","tid":866271,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:55:25.000Z","msg":"個站頭幾日已經殘到仆街<br />\n啲地下好多跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n唔講以為開左20年<br />\n一定係用垃圾料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc59e4b5475165fbe33e465f7608d3450fa1d569","tid":866271,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:51:39.000Z","msg":"設計無美感 搵鬼佬都無用"},{"pid":"6778b72003f7ddcf5df03c3d1c76bf5896e28caf","tid":866271,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc59e4b5475165fbe33e465f7608d3450fa1d569","tid":866271,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T21:51:39.000Z","msg":"設計無美感 搵鬼佬都無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"Aggrr"}]}